com.instabug.library.Instabug.Builder:
The core Instabug SDK class.
 Logging
The Instabug SDK can provide logs that may be helpful if you want to test out the
 integration or trace the SDK process. To turn it on, just enable debugging by setting
 Instabug.DEBUG = true;

 For more info, please refer to.Logging
